data.description: *What an amazing retreat! CAN YOU SAY 5 BEDROOMS ON lush wooded land + W/POOL! Completely remod 2024, all new appliances, paint, kitchen, 1st floor laundry and first floor bedroom if needed. This hidden gem is a great get-away with only a 30 min drive to downtown and all fwys/ but also a stones throw from the lake and more. Get best of both worlds with this Cape Cod Remod. The breezeway can be easily converted to make a 3 seasons area. Connecting the home to the 1.5 car garage this 10x6 outdoor space gives an option to expand the outdoors -in... if desired. Some original hardwood floor is still exposed on the first floor to retain the history, huge lot 110x360/ leaves the heart to the imagination, pole barn? in ground pool? ideas are endless, even though the home has been remod the owners left a lot of room for the new owners to make it their own. Come on in, enjoy space, privacy and land. All appliances are included. Easy to show please contact with any questions. Pack your bags and enjoy this retreat and space.
